      <h2>Description</h2>
      <p>
                  Rat Simulator is a game about a rat's life in a household. No longer do you need to wonder what they get up to when humans are around, as this state-of-the-art computer simulation models the complete rat experience. Consume food and wreck destruction in the house so you can build a ratâ€™s paradise.  
